The Cost-Utility of Total Hip Arthroplasty: Earlier Intervention, Improved 
Economics.

Lavernia CJ(1), Iacobelli DA(2), Brooks L(3), Villa JM(2).

Author information:
(1)The Center for Advanced Orthopedics at Larkin Hospital South Miami, Florida.
(2)The Center for Advanced Orthopedics at Larkin Hospital South Miami, Florida; 
Arthritis Surgery Research Foundation South Miami, Florida.
(3)Arthritis Surgery Research Foundation South Miami, Florida.

We estimated the cost of Quality-Adjusted-Life-Years gained according to 
